---
title: Poblano & Portobello Fajitas with Fresh Guacamole
description: These fajitas are piled high with toppings: homemade refried beans, guacamole, and plenty of sautéed veggies. Poblano brings a nice, mild heat to the plate - be sure to cool it off with some tangy sour cream. Who knows, maybe Fajita Fridays will become the new Taco Tuesdays!
